Hattie Winston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hattie_Winston 0 Hattie Mae Winston (born March 3, 1945) is an American television, film and Broadway actress best known for her role as Margaret on Becker and as a prominent cast member of the PBS children's series The Electric Company.
